title: Connection Course by Mark Manson
description:
The basic premise of this course is to teach you how to be able to engage people on an emotional level. To that end, it succeeds. There's a number of different conversational techniques and structures taught that will get you thinking and communicating in a way that is more emotionally relevant to people. You'll learn how to get people telling you more personal stories about themselves, which in turn will create a stronger connection between you.
Take note that this course is not specifically aimed at improving your success with women. It is about relating on a deeper level with people in general. The information here is really solid for helping you connect better with women, but is not useful if you are looking for a product that focuses on meeting women or developing sexual relationships with them
